metadata.name: ASCESE
metadata.description:
As one era ends, another is born— in Metaeden, where Earth’s density is erased and heightened perception is explored. Giada, Adaeze and Keiko are the first to immerse themselves in this alternate existence. Their awareness level is trackable and increases with advancement.

Episode #1: ASCESE observes the initial shock response to such a paradisiacal environment. It feels good. No! It feels amazing. 

Spoiler alert: it’s not a total cakewalk. Their adjustment and assimilation shifts from bliss to internal chaos in episode #2, out next month. 

All collectors receive a custom avatar and cameo in the final episode, #7.
